  "subject": "Fix regression on patching any objects other than AAI resources",
  "commit_message": "Fix regression on patching any objects other than AAI resources\n\nDue to fact that for patching some specific headers was set (due to fact\nA&AI requires that) all other resources couldn't be patched. That's a quick\nfix for that issue\n\nIssue-ID: TEST-404\nSigned-off-by: Michal Jagiello <michal.jagiello@t-mobile.pl>\nChange-Id: I79d70d5bb6541db1c8b1b10db2d9091e16211846\n",
